<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.187488>
    dc:description "FIGURES 13 – 18. Wings. 13: Paradoxa fusca Marshall, dorsal view. 14: Sigmoleia melanoxantha Edwards, ventral view. 15: Sigmoleia similis sp. n., ventral view. 16: Sigmoleia separata sp. n., dorsal view. 17: Sigmoleia peterjohnsi sp. n., vental view. 18: Cycloneura triangulata Tonnoir, ventral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/187488/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.187496>
    dc:description "FIGURES 65 – 70. Morphology in Sigmoleia spp. 65 – 68: Sigmoleia separata sp. n.. 69 – 70: Sigmoleia peterjohnsi sp. n. 65: Male terminalia, ventral view. 66: Tegmen, ventral view. 67: Terminalia, dorsal view. 68: Flagellomeres 1 – 5, lateral view, male left, female right. 69: Male terminalia, ventral view. 70: Male terminalia, dorsal view. Length of scale bar = 0.05 mm (for 66) and 0.1 mm (for 65, 67 – 70)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/187496/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

